== Notes ==

For those '''arriving by Eurostar/TGV''' there is a direct hourly train service (taking 36 minutes) from Brussels Midi/Zuid to the local railway station ('''Hoeilaart''') 900 metres walk from the hotel.  This is ''included for free'' as part of your existing Eurostar ticket, as Eurostar tickets from the UK are issued to '''Any Belgian Station''':
